message.body: Hi. Where are u located?
Fawkes, are u there?
Hi jetskiwr! I'm sorry, was in a meeting. I'm located in the San Francisco bay area. How about yourself?
No problem. I'm in Phoenix, AZ.
Oh cool, you're on PT too! Are you a student, or a working professional?
Lol. I guess i'm a working professional. I'm a mobile DJ and a promotional specialist. It keeps me busy
You?
I'm an engineer working in a Silicon Valley startup. How are you affiliated to Penn?
No real affiliation. Just signed up with their site a long time ago to earn some extra money on communication project
I see. Where're you from, jetskiwr?
I grew up in El Paso, TX, and was born in Florida. Have u lived in Cali all ur life?
Btw, i'm going to be absent for a bit to do some yardwork. I'll catch back up with u when i'm done
I was a student at Penn. Graduated in May 2012 and then came to CA. Sure, talk to you later!
Oh, gotcha! I graduated from AZ State U back in 2004. You're a youngin!:-)
Well, I attended grad school at Penn but yeah I'm young, I guess :P I'm mid-20s. What do you do in your spare time?
I work out a lot. Im training for a half Ironman in Oct. I attend a lot of concerts. I love dancing and karaoke. Camping and traveling. In fact, I'm leav
ing for the Dominican Republic for a week today.
What occupies your spare tome?
Oops...time
(1/2)Wow, that's amazing! I don't get any spare time! I put in around 12 hours of work everyday. On the weekends, however, I spend time learning/playing the
(2/2)guitar, going out on adventure hikes/bikes and making cool science projects right at home!
